<L>__{exterior chateau night}
<A>__{the driveway and motorcourt are filled with cars. a formal dress party is in progress... a private reception for a middle eastern dignitary. tuxedoes men escort their diamond encrusted ladies through the huge front doors, where they doff their overcoats and are politely scanned with hand held metal detectors by white gloved security staffers. the walled perimeter of the house runs along the lake, forming a kind of rampart. there is an opening, to a kind of waterway or canal, which connects to the private docks inside the grounds. there is a steel grating across the opening. the bars disappear down into the thin ice of early winter. with the house visible bg, we crane down below the parapet wall along which a guard is a white exposure suit is walking... down along the dark wall to the grating... tilting down to see a glow pulsing under the ice.}
